{"type": "article", "id": 3980, "title": "Polygon 手表", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-01T07:46:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233227q1xuLF27OtBcaV3H.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t总部位于台湾的设计工作室 Chi and Chi 日前推出一款名为「Polygon」的手表，延续了该工作室一贯的极简主义美学，用最精简的形式服务于最核心的功能。设计团队赋予了 Polygon 独特的多边形的几何边框，为用户提供了与众不同的触感。而表盘内的设计元素也仅以直线与圆圈进行呈现。Polygon 由 PVD 金色表壳与皮革表带混搭制作而成，表带提供黑色、棕色与银色 3 种选择，定价 115 美元，<a href=\"http://www.chiandchi.com/collections/allproducts\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233225Y8d43hXC5BT7OFLS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233225QONX30nytvIMCSHc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233226ceKA2EV9zWP8FGk4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233226p3ziJwZ8nHIC7EbW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}